    <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3 class="question">What flavors of Pepsi are available? <span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></h3>
            <div class="answer">Pepsi offers a variety of flavors including Pepsi Zero Sugar, Diet Pepsi, Pepsi Caffeine Free, and classic Pepsi with sugar.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3 class="question">Is Pepsi suitable for vegetarians and vegans? <span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></h3>
            <div class="answer">Yes, Pepsi products are suitable for vegetarians and vegans as they do not contain any animal-derived ingredients.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3 class="question">How much caffeine is in Pepsi? <span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></h3>
            <div class="answer">A standard 12 fl oz (355 mL) can of Pepsi contains about 38 mg of caffeine.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3 class="question">Does Pepsi have any sugar-free options? <span class="arrow">&#9660;</span></h3>
            <div class="answer">Yes, Pepsi offers sugar-free options like Pepsi Zero Sugar and Diet Pepsi for those looking to reduce their sugar intake.</div>
